  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The project includes /package.json and /contracts/package.json and publishes `@openzeppelin/contracts` and `openzeppelin-solidity` respectively. I'm sure there is some good, well-thought-out reason for this.\r\n\r\nThe two files contribute the same `description` of `Secure Smart Contract library for Solidity` and look mostly the same inside.\r\n\r\nTo improve maintainability of these two files, some note should be added inside (e.g. `\"note\":`) each describing the difference between the two files or where responsibility of one ends and the other starts.",
